entries.journal_entry_description: Somehow Stormtroopers have managed to survive within the walls of the research facility. Find them and get a situation report.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: [Guri] You should locate the Stormtrooper contingent that boy mentioned. They may be of use to your mission.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: [Guri] I found an Imperial record of a Zahara Cody but nothing of her working on a prison barge. I also found a criminal record for Trig Longo. Very interesting.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Travel to the Imperial Research and Prison Facility and find the Stormtroopers Trig Longo mentioned.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: [Guri] Looks like you have found what is left of the facility. Hopefully the Stormtrooper contingent have managed to survive. Use your stolen authorization to convince them you work for Darth Vader.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Search the interior of the facility for the Stormtroopers.
